sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant FE as React Frontend
    participant API as FastAPI Backend
    participant GIS as GIS Service<br/>(Shapely + pyproj)
    participant DB as MongoDB
    participant WS as WebSocket Manager

    User->>FE: Click "Recalculate Coverage"
    FE->>API: POST /api/v1/projects/{id}/coverage
    API->>API: Require Owner or Editor role
    API->>DB: Fetch all CameraInstances for project<br/>(fov_geojson fields)
    DB-->>API: CameraInstance[]
    API->>DB: Fetch all Zones where purpose=coverage_area
    DB-->>API: Zone[]

    API->>GIS: compute_coverage_stats(fov_polygons, zone_polygons)
    GIS->>GIS: Project WGS84 → local UTM (pyproj)
    GIS->>GIS: Union all FOV polygons (Shapely unary_union)
    GIS->>GIS: Intersect union with coverage_area zones
    GIS->>GIS: Compute overlaps (pairwise FOV intersections)
    GIS->>GIS: Detect gaps (zone area minus covered area)
    GIS->>GIS: Reproject results back → WGS84 GeoJSON
    GIS-->>API: CoverageStats { total_covered_m2,<br/>overlap_geojson, gap_geojson, computed_at }

    API->>DB: Update project.coverage_stats + updated_at
    DB-->>API: OK
    API->>WS: broadcast coverage_recalculated<br/>to all project room members
    WS-->>FE: { type: coverage_recalculated, payload: CoverageStats }
    API-->>FE: 200 OK — CoverageStats

    FE->>FE: Update coverageSlice in Zustand
    FE->>FE: Render overlap + gap GeoJSON layers on map
    FE->>FE: Display total_covered_m2 in stats panel
